page.title: 12Leafield Landmarks
page.content: 1.Masts. The masts are a common sight in Leafield.We have a large mast behind the butcher's shop.It is for calls to the Police,Ambulance or Fire service. Nobody wanted it to be put up because they said it spoilt the village.I don't think it spoils the village as much as the new houses do. 2.The New House. The new house is north west from the school.It has been there for a year.It is yellow and ugly and one side is thinner than the other.The bricks don't look right and it's out of shape.Nobody lives in it yet.
